      |--- spkcompiler
      |    ==============
      |       | Makefile.am
      |       | main.cpp
      |       | ...cpp
      |       | ...h
      |       |
      |       |--- nonmem
      |            ======
      |                Nonmem...cpp
      |                Nonmem...h
      |
      |--- tests
      |    =====
      |       | Makefile.am
      |       |
